{"title":"搭建LAMP环境","uid":"065300218eb4a63be27d42f44bfa37db","slug":"搭建LAMP环境","date":"2018-01-21T10:11:41.000Z","updated":"2022-10-19T10:05:40.398Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/搭建LAMP环境.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://gimg2.baidu.com/image_search/src=http%3A%2F%2Foss.aliyuncs.com%2Fphotogallery%2Fphoto%2F1930532890589852%2F955%2F9f1021cc-faaf-43ea-b01e-570e71595339.png&refer=http%3A%2F%2Foss.aliyuncs.com&app=2002&size=f9999,10000&q=a80&n=0&g=0n&fmt=auto?sec=1668765919&t=045e3e0d0039ddcbb644b6f52eb784e9","content":"<h1 id=\"1搭建-MySQL-数据库\"><a href=\"#1搭建-MySQL-数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1搭建 MySQL 数据库\"></a>1搭建 MySQL 数据库</h1><p>安装 MySQL<br>使用 yum 安装 MySQL：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">yum install mysql-server -y</code></pre>\n<p>安装完成后，启动 MySQL 服务：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">service mysqld restart</code></pre>\n<p>设置 MySQL 账户 root 密码：[?]</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;mysqladmin -u root password &#39;Password&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"2安装-Apache-服务\"><a href=\"#2安装-Apache-服务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2安装 Apache 服务\"></a>2安装 Apache 服务</h1><p>安装 Apache<br>使用 yum 安装 Apache</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum install httpd -y</code></pre>\n<p>启动 Apache 服务：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">service httpd start</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"3安装-PHP\"><a href=\"#3安装-PHP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3安装 PHP\"></a>3安装 PHP</h1><p>安装 PHP 和 PHP-MYSQL 支持工具：<br>使用 yum 安装 PHP：[?]</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum install php php-mysql -y</code></pre>\n<p>CentOS 6 默认已经安装了 php-mysql，下面命令执行的可能会提示已经安装。</p>\n<h1 id=\"4检查安装是否成功\"><a href=\"#4检查安装是否成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4检查安装是否成功\"></a>4检查安装是否成功</h1><p>检验 PHP 是否安装成功<br>我们在 /var/www/html 目录下创建一个info.php文件来检查php是否安装成功，示例代码参考如下</p>\n<p>示例代码：/var/www/html/info.php</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&lt;?php phpinfo(); ?&gt;</code></pre>\n<p>重启 Apache 服务：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">service httpd restart</code></pre>\n<p>此时，访问 http://&lt;您的 CVM IP 地址&gt;/info.php 可浏览到我们刚刚创建的 info.php 页面了</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"1搭建 MySQL 数据库安装 MySQL使用 yum 安装 MySQL： yum install mysql-server -y 安装完成后，启动 MySQL 服务： service mysqld restart 设置 MySQL 账户 root 密码：[?] &#x2F;us...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":658,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"},{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":2,"path":"api/tags/教程.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-MySQL-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1搭建 MySQL 数据库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-Apache-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2安装 Apache 服务</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-PHP\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3安装 PHP</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4检查安装是否成功</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Johnny","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"Welcome to my blog <br/> I'm Johnny Bao.-a DevOps.","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Nginx快速入门","